  <h2>The principle</h2>
  <p>A commitment made in the members' name should follow from members being informed and deciding for themselves, not come before it. This is the same standard the Circle asks every council to meet: members see the information, members decide, and only then is the Nation's name committed. See the <a href="/standard">shared transparency standard and records request</a>.</p>

